    </Button>
  </div>
</header>

<section class='max-w-screen-sm mx-auto p-4 mt-10 mb-4'>
  <h1 class='text-center text-3xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4 md:text-5xl'>UUID Tools</h1>
  <p class='max-w-screen-sm text-lg text-muted-foreground sm:text-xl'>
    Convert between common UUID formats, generate new values and analyze their byte components.
    <a class='underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-accent-foreground transition-colors' href='#about'>
      What is UUID?
    </a>
  </p>
</section>
